            "title": "劉丹揸車被網民衝出阻截險象環生︰心入面爆緊粗  譚輝智認拍劇背對白比唱歌難",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"劉丹揸車離開電視城被網民衝出阻截︰心入面爆緊粗  譚輝智認拍劇背對白比唱歌難\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/6d60f7d941a4a38adff683788cf0ab02/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250416/_2025041615380578642.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">劉丹揸車離開電視城被網民衝出阻截︰心入面爆緊粗  譚輝智認拍劇背對白比唱歌難</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>劉丹、呂慧儀、滕麗名、單立文、姚焯菲等在將軍澳電視城宣傳處境劇《愛·回家之開心速遞》，活動上宣布《中年好聲音》第2季人氣王譚輝智將加入愛回家大家庭，現場眾人更齊玩遊戲。\n\n</p><h2>劉丹䒐䒏被網民攔車</h2>\n<p>劉丹與譚輝智齊齊受訪，4月中，有網民在電視城外捕獲劉丹駕車離開，並將片段分享到小紅書，寫道「丹爺80多歲還在開車」，劉丹被指80歲仍每日駕車代步，又被指反應慢；劉丹即反問譚輝智自己是否遲頓？譚輝智即笑指劉丹開車比他勁。劉丹指從小到大都開車，沒難度，坦言當刻有點䒐䒏，開車離開電視城突然被人攔住，反問發生意外有危險由誰負責，「其實我心裡面講緊粗口，開車出來當然要望左望右，他們又突然圍上來，這樣就被寫是反應遲頓，講講吓我都得啖笑！」劉丹指自己沒嬲，一家人都信佛沒太大脾氣，面對新聞覺得沒需要攤開來講。譚輝智表示上月開始拍攝，未知是客串還是常駐角色，笑言要看演出表現，今次和劉丹的「熊家人」有很多對手戲，很大壓力，大讚劉丹演技犀利，在電視上看不覺得，現場感受到對方的專業。劉丹指譚輝智是唱得之人，絕對醒目，覺得他有一定演技，作為新人有進步，譚輝智即自嘲有好大進步空間，又指演處境劇有一定難度，比唱歌難，背對白也有點吃力，自認多NG。劉丹指譚輝智會觀察其他演員，學習反應。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4198356/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"劉丹、譚輝智、呂慧儀、滕麗名、單立文、吳偉豪、姚焯菲等在將軍澳電視城宣傳處境劇《愛·回家之開心速遞》。\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/68cdc0e793cb597c36881b732f62307a/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-16_at_14_04_57.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"img_caption\">\n      劉丹、譚輝智、呂慧儀、滕麗名、單立文、吳偉豪、姚焯菲等在將軍澳電視城宣傳處境劇《愛·回家之開心速遞》。\n    </div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4198467/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"4月中，有網民在電視城外捕獲劉丹駕車離開，場面驚險。\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/bb16f305dd9102b3a7b3484492f3aceb/2025-04/AEz2nPOzcSQaGRNFWbhNOlhhahTwxQ1dZvy_92b8v_c.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"img_caption\">\n      4月中，有網民在電視城外捕獲劉丹駕車離開，場面驚險。\n    </div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4198357/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"活動上眾人齊玩遊戲，宣布《中年好聲音》第2季人氣王譚輝智加入愛回家大家庭。\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9a215c0d5bcbdedfbf0529aa191d7ec2/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-16_at_14_04_58_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"img_caption\">\n      活動上眾人齊玩遊戲，宣布《中年好聲音》第2季人氣王譚輝智加入愛回家大家庭。\n    </div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4198417/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"譚輝智是唱得之人，獻唱《慶餘年2》主題曲，張若昀、李沁「飯碗CP」再度登場。\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c3d11011f2b1dbce0207583cca161c92/2025-04/coverr_1.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"img_caption\">\n      譚輝智是唱得之人，獻唱《慶餘年2》主題曲，張若昀、李沁「飯碗CP」再度登場。\n    </div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4198358/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"《中年好聲音》第2季人氣王譚輝智加入愛回家大家庭。\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/92ab288ee538c7c0af3834d0ea740d17/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-16_at_14_04_58.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"img_caption\">\n      《中年好聲音》第2季人氣王譚輝智加入愛回家大家庭。\n    </div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4198359/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"劉丹指譚輝智會觀察其他演員，學習反應。\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e16a550a14b25d6aa8a106dabab5033f/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-16_at_14_05_00_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"img_caption\">\n      劉丹指譚輝智會觀察其他演員，學習反應。\n    </div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4198360/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"81歲劉丹揸車被指反應慢，佢話得啖笑。\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fc396ebcd0d4067cba161ccd925b4919/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-16_at_14_05_00.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"img_caption\">\n      81歲劉丹揸車被指反應慢，佢話得啖笑。\n    </div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4198361/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"譚輝智表示上月開始拍攝，未知是客串還是常駐角色，笑言要看演出表現。\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/647ffb9f52585eb03b590c03c81605f9/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-16_at_14_05_01.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"img_caption\">\n      譚輝智表示上月開始拍攝，未知是客串還是常駐角色，笑言要看演出表現。\n    </div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4198362/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"譚輝智話背對白有難度，成日NG。\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d477f314ace3a757631d6737c995dfe8/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-16_at_14_05_02_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"img_caption\">\n      譚輝智話背對白有難度，成日NG。\n    </div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4198363/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"譚輝智讚81歲劉丹手車好勁。\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/935a30e44bdbb516b2ef4fc1adb95be2/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-16_at_14_05_02.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"img_caption\">\n      譚輝智讚81歲劉丹手車好勁。\n    </div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2064263/即時-娛樂-劉丹揸車被網民衝出阻截險象環生-心入面爆緊粗-譚輝智認拍劇背對白比唱歌難",
