        {
            "title": "無業漢認葵涌工廈內營運無牌牙醫診所等3罪 還押至4月30日判刑",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"報稱無業的被告李漢山，承認無牌從事牙醫執業等罪候懲。資料圖片\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/f456272d8c3be5d4c381d96f3c67f43e/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250416/_2025041616391256435.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">報稱無業的被告李漢山，承認無牌從事牙醫執業等罪候懲。資料圖片</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>中年無業漢去年11月在葵涌工業大廈内經營無牌牙醫診所，診所被搜出大量牙醫工具、儀器及受管制藥物等，被控未經註冊為牙醫的人從事牙科執業等3罪。涉案無業漢於西九龍裁判法院認罪，裁判官王證瑜將被告暫時收監，先索閱社會服務令報告，案件押後至4月30日判刑。\n\n</p>\n<p>54歲被告李漢山，報稱無業，被控未經註冊為牙醫的人從事牙科執業、管有第I部毒藥及管有抗生素條例適用的物質罪。控罪指被告於2024年11月20日，在葵昌中心406室内並非註冊牙醫，而在香港從事牙科執業；另並非按照藥劑業及毒藥條例條文的規定，管有4個膠袋載有40個小玻璃瓶合共載有73.3克液體內含阿替卡因及5個銀箔紙包裝合共載有50顆膠囊內含加巴噴丁；及管有/控制《抗生素條例》適用的162顆膠褒，內含鄰氯青霉素，為青霉素的一種衍生物。\n\n</p>\n<p>案件編號：WKCC612/2025<br/>\n法庭記者：黃巧兒\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2064290/即時-港聞-無業漢認葵涌工廈內營運無牌牙醫診所等3罪-還押至4月30日判刑",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-16 16:46:08",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "又中又英｜Gorgeous head of hair",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/218ede40d799b316e4077eb89a24f506/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250416/_2025041616290041863.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>How often should you wash your hair? Dermatologists say there\\'s no rule of thumb. Your shampoo frequency depends on your hair type. A dermatologist is a skin doctor. The expression \"rule of thumb\" means a method of doing things based on experience and common sense, not science. Dermatologists say people with thin or oily hair should shampoo daily or every two to three days. People with thick or curly hair should shampoo about once a week. Shampooing too often is not good because it washes away the natural oils in hair. \n\n</p>\n<p>US President Donald Trump takes meticulous care of his hair. If you take meticulous care of something, it means you pay great attention to every detail of it. Trump often boasts that he has beautiful and perfect hair. He once told friends he has a \"gorgeous head of hair\". The word \"gorgeous\" means very beautiful or very attractive. Trump has said it takes about an hour for his hair to dry after shampooing. He doesn\\'t use a hairdryer. He then meticulously combs his hair to make it look like what he describes as \"perfect\".\n\n</p>\n<p>Trump has long complained about the low water pressure in showers. He said it takes about 15 minutes to wet his hair because of the low water pressure. A 1990s law restricted water flow to 2.5 gallons per minute to save water. Former President Barack Obama ordered that the 2.5 gallons rule should remain even for shower heads with several nozzles (outlets). Trump reversed that in his first term, but Joe Biden reinstated the rule when he was president. Trump found time last week despite his tariff war to sign an Executive Order that every nozzle in a shower head can have 2.5 gallons of water per minute!\n\n</p>\n<p>你會隔多久洗一次頭？皮膚科醫生（dermatologists）說那是沒有法則（rule of thumb）的。你的洗髮頻密度取決於你的髮質。A dermatologist就是皮膚科醫生。習語 rule of thumb是指基於經驗或常理而非科學所得的法則。皮膚科醫生（dermatologists）說，幼軟或油性髮質的人士應每天又或二至三天洗一次頭；粗厚或捲曲髮質的，則應一周洗一次。洗頭洗得太頻密是不好的，因為它會洗走頭髮中天然產生的油脂。\n\n</p>\n<p>美國總統唐納德‧特朗普對自己的頭髮則是關懷備至的（meticulous care）。若你 take meticulous care of something，意即你對某事物照顧周到、無微不至。特朗普常自誇他擁有亮麗完美的秀髮，他有次還告訴朋友，他有一頭「華麗（gorgeous）的濃髮」。Gorgeous是指非常漂亮或吸引的。特朗普也曾說，洗頭後要用上一個小時去弄乾，他也不用風筒吹乾，而是一絲不苟地（meticulously）梳理頭髮，令其看上去是他形容為「完美」的髮型。\n\n</p>\n<p>特朗普對於淋浴水壓太低已經投訴很久了。他說，因為水壓太低，得用上十五分鐘才能弄濕頭髮。一個一九九零年代的法例規定，為了節省用水，出水每分鐘不能多於二點五加侖。前總統巴拉克‧奧巴馬下令，即使是有許多噴嘴（nozzles）的花灑頭，亦要維持這個二點五加侖出水量的規限。特朗普在第一任當總統時撤銷了，但祖‧拜登在任時又恢復了規定。特朗普上星期在貿易戰以外，仍騰出時間去簽署行政命令，容許花灑頭的每一個噴嘴（nozzle）也能有每分鐘二點五加侖的出水上限！\n\n</p>\n<p><a class=\"__cf_email__\" data-cfemail=\"c0ada9a3aba3a8b5a780a7ada1a9aceea3afad\" href=\"/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection\">[email protected]</a><br/>\nMichael Chugani褚簡寧<br/>\n中譯：七刻\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2064286/即時-港聞-又中又英-Gorgeous-head-of-hair",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-16 16:31:39",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "羅兵咸據報退出10多個國家業務 避免醜聞重演",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"羅兵咸據報退出10多個國家業務 避免醜聞重演\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/98e5386c82881d16802c11f57601bec6/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250416/_2025041616225475206.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">羅兵咸據報退出10多個國家業務 避免醜聞重演</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>據英國《金融時報》報道，羅兵咸已停止在十多個被其全球負責人視為規模太小、風險太大或無利可圖的國家開展業務，以避免影響公司聲譽的醜聞重演。\n\n</p><h2>近年損失逾三分之一業務</h2>\n<p>報道指出，由於與當地合作夥伴的分歧日益加劇，羅兵咸於本月初與其在非洲法語區的10家成員事務所終止了合作關係。這些事務所的領導人表示，近年來由於羅兵咸全球高層施壓要求停止為高風險客戶提供服務，導致他們損失逾三分之一業務，並於去年開始商討退出事宜。\n\n</p>\n<p>根據羅兵咸的實體登記冊和當地新聞報道，羅兵咸與其在津巴布韋、馬拉維和斐濟的成員公司斷絕關係僅僅數月之後，就敲定了終止合作事宜。曾任羅兵咸負責合規事務的前合夥人指出，儘管非洲地區的收入與其他地區相比較低，但國際領導層仍投入大量時間關注非洲業務。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2064284/即時-財經-羅兵咸據報退出10多個國家業務-避免醜聞重演",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-16 16:31:39",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "運沙船菲律賓海翻側  1中國船員亡10人疑困引擎室",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"翻側的運沙船，已致1名中國船員死亡，尚有10名船員懷疑被困船內。FB@Coast Guard District Southern Tagalog\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/78301730e90f2e285378ff1849fbdfdb/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250416/_2025041616220451437.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">翻側的運沙船，已致1名中國船員死亡，尚有10名船員懷疑被困船內。FB@Coast Guard District Southern Tagalog</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>菲律賓中部海域有一艘運沙船翻側，已造成1名中國船員死亡、10人失蹤，14人獲救。搜索行動仍在繼續。\n\n</p><h2>潛水員準備水下切割搜救</h2>\n<p>綜合媒體報道，隸屬菲律賓砂石公司「Keen Peak Corp」的運沙船「Hong Hai 16」15日下午5時20分在西明多羅省（Occidental Mindoro）黎薩鎮（Rizal）水域翻覆。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"翻側的運沙船，已致1名中國船員死亡，尚有10名船員懷疑被困船內。FB@Coast Guard District Southern Tagalog\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d673a2b3dce2a34c5843f13624266ab5/2025-04/New_Project_hrtfjknld.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        翻側的運沙船，已致1名中國船員死亡，尚有10名船員懷疑被困船內。FB@Coast Guard District Southern Tagalog\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>運沙船上有25名船員，13人為菲律賓籍、12人為中國籍。目前證實，有1名中國船員死亡、6名菲人和8名中國人獲救，仍有10人待搜救。\n\n</p>\n<p>菲律賓海岸防衛隊16日報告指，10名失蹤者中，分別有7名菲人和3名中國人。失聯船員可能受困在「直立且部分進水」的引擎室內，特別行動組正準備潛水、展開水下切割作業。\n\n</p>\n<p>海岸防衛隊稱，事發當時海象不算惡劣，接獲通報後，立即出動快艇到場搜救，同時查看漏油污染環境的可能性。\n\n</p>\n<p>黎薩鎮「減災與管理辦公室」主任索里亞諾（Mary Jolence Soriano）指稱，沒有人知道這艘船已經抵達，大家都很訝異。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2064283/即時-國際-運沙船菲律賓海翻側-1中國船員亡10人疑困引擎室",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-16 16:31:39",
